      Cohan, Arman  and
      Dumas, Jennifer  and
      Elazar, Yanai  and
      Gu, Yuling  and
      Hessel, Jack  and
      Khot, Tushar  and
      Merrill, William  and
      Morrison, Jacob  and
      Muennighoff, Niklas  and
      Naik, Aakanksha  and
      Nam, Crystal  and
      Peters, Matthew  and
